lore: A nerf pistol with a steady rate of fire and moderate damage. Easy to handle, easy to move with; a great choice for anyone.
Mega dart pistol that deals heavy damage and pierces through zombies. Deadly at medium range, though it takes some skill to handle. Mega darts stun their target briefly.
A compact Mega dart pistol. Deals high damage and can be reloaded quickly. Its small size makes it very easy to run with, but very inaccurate. Mega darts stun their target briefly.
Pump action shotgun that fires several darts at once. Annihilates zombies up close, and remains reliable at medium range.
Lightweight double barrel shotgun that hits extremely hard. Shreds through zombies at point blank range; excellent for aggressive hit and run maneuvers. Not suited for range.
Mega dart slug shotgun that can pulverize zombies at medium range. Accurate, but somewhat heavy and cumbersome to wield. Mega darts stun their target briefly.
Steady rapid fire blaster that remains accurate at long ranges. Ideal for those who want consistency from a distance.
Powerful full auto blaster with a high rate of fire. Deals high damage, but extremely heavy. Front-mounted shield provides protection at the cost of accuracy.
Highly accurate marksman rifle with an extended barrel for long range combat. Moderate fire rate allows for quick follow up shots.
Powerful sniper rifle that tears through zombies at extreme ranges. Pinpoint accuracy and incredible damage, but not very mobile.
Slower but fairly hard hitting pistol.  Zombiestrike darts inflict Wither on zombies, dealing damage over time.

Reliable marksman rifle that excels at taking down armored zombies. Shorter barrel increases mobility at the cost of range. Zombiestrike darts inflict Wither on zombies, dealing extra damage over time.
Two-in-one blaster that can be used in full auto or as a semi-auto shotgun. Different firing modes allow for great versatility.
High caliber sniper rifle that vaporizes everything in its path. If it’s still alive afterwards, it won’t be moving for a long time. Mega darts stun their target briefly.
Belt-fed blaster with an immense rate of fire. Deals unrivaled damage but lacks accuracy. Darts pierce through zombies, annihilating crowds with ease.
Unique heavy full auto blaster. Darts travel quickly and pierce through targets. Very stable when firing. Zombiestrike darts inflict Wither on zombies, dealing extra damage over time.
Long range pump shotgun with great stability. Fires slowly, but guaranteed to destroy whatever it hits. Zombiestrike darts inflict Wither on zombies, dealing extra damage over time.
Full auto Mega dart blaster. Low dart velocity, but slows tough zombies to a crawl with sustained fire. Mega darts stun their target briefly.
Large Mega dart pistol with a moderate rate of fire. Excellent for providing support and holding back crowds of zombies, though not incredibly accurate. Mega darts stun their target briefly.
Lightweight pistol with great range and accuracy. Silencer conceals position when firing. Extremely easy to move with.
Highly reliable long range rifle. Uses ammo very efficiently, and darts are always on target. Accustrike darts weaken zombies, making them do less damage.
Close range full auto blaster with extreme damage output. Removed stock sacrifices accuracy for greater mobility. Accustrike darts weaken zombies, making them do less damage.
Reliable full auto blaster with an underbarrel grenade launcher. Grenades do high damage to crowds of zombies. Accustrike darts weaken zombies, making them do less damage.
Long range rifle with extremely high dart velocity. Can use both regular and Mega darts. Can pierce through dozens of zombies.
The Nexus Pros little brother, offering similar power in a smaller package. Compact size offers mobility, but sacrifices accuracy and reload speed.

A rare variant of the Roughcut with unique upgrades. Tuned for maximum slam-fire performance, fires much faster than normal at the cost of accuracy.  Zombiestrike darts inflict Wither on zombeis, dealing extra damage over time.
Heavy hitting shotgun with a slow fire rate, but very wide spread.  Deals very high damage upfront, and can take out several zombies in one hit.
Giant rapid fire mega shotgun, shredding through crowds with ease at the cost of increased ammo consumption
Efficient full auto blaster with balanced stopping power, firerate, and ammo consumption.
Proof that a blue Twinshock can exist, and a symbol of power for the Udub HvZ Club before the apocalypse.  Only the truly worthy may wield it.
Tactical full auto blaster with high fire rate and accuracy.  Better version of the Stryfe.
Recovered from the icy hands of a fallen survivor, this frozen Magnus has been repaired, firing darts cold enough to freeze zombies solid!
Extremely light weight with high melee damage, and can be thrown infinitely.  All around good backup for zombies that get too close.
The yellow caution tape pattern means keep out!  Too bad the zombies wont listen...
DAKKA DAKKA DAKKA!
Despite this water gun's harmless appearance, it turns out that zombies hate getting wet, rendering them non-threats.  Inflicts Weakness on zombies.
Ever wanted a pocket rocket?  Then the Thunderblast is for you, if you are willing to carry the extra weight.
A very specialized explosive weapon with high damage, but takes forever to load, so carry a strong backup.
An experiemental Biosquad blaster able to spray zombie repellent and occasional darts with the alternative fire.  Inflicts Wither and Weakness on zombies
An experiemental Biosquad blaster able to spray zombie repellent or a shotgun blast with the alternative fire.  Inflicts Wither and Weakness on zombies.
Similar to the Hammershot, except that the alternative fire can heal teammates.
